@startuml
|User|
start
: Click on Update button;
|System|
: Display form to update Supplier information;
|User|
: Fill needed information;
: Click on Confirm button;
|System|
: Validate new information;
if (Valid?) then (Yes)
  : Update Supplier information to the database;
  : Update Supplier details screen;
else (No)
  : Display error message;
endif
stop
@enduml
